### Set HTML dir attribute for AvailabilitySettings atom

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/faq.mdx

To ensure the toggle animation works correctly within the AvailabilitySettings atom, you need to set the 'dir' attribute on the '<html>' element to 'ltr'. This is a specific requirement for this UI component's functionality.

```html
<html dir="ltr"> ... </html>
```

